sections.heading: Auctioneers; compliance with Nebraska Real Estate License Act; required
sections.text: All auctioneers of any state shall comply with the requirements of the Nebraska Real Estate License Act before conducting a sale of real estate in this state.SourceLaws 1953, c. 339, ยง 3, p. 1112;Laws 2009, LB30, ยง 15;Laws 2022,
